      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but my doctor is super dismissive and always just says \"wait it out\" which isn't helping. i really just want to give the natural route a shot because the side effects are making it hard to function. if i just taper off the zoloft slowly over a week and then start the st johns wort, is that a safe way to do it? i just need to know if the herb actually works the same way so i can feel better about making the switch.",
